text: Renaissance is a political party in Monaco that represents the interests of SBM employees.Landslide victory for Horizon Monaco Riviera Times, 11 February 2013 They won 10.67% of the popular vote, and 1 out of 24 seats in the legislative elections held on February 10, 2013. The seat was held by Eric Elena.
